      <span class="verse-number" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Ensign:Serif&quot;, McKay, &quot;McKay ldsLat&quot;, Palatino, &quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;, &quot;Palatino Bold&quot;, Palatino-Bold, Pahoran, &quot;Pahoran ldsLat&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans Myanmar&quot;, NotoSansMyanmar, SaysetthaldsLao, NotoSerifTamil, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">38</span><span>&nbsp;</span>これがいちばん<ruby
        style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><rb
          style="box-sizing: border-box;">大切</rb><rt style="box-sizing: border-box;">たいせつ</rt></ruby>な、<ruby
        style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><rb
          style="box-sizing: border-box;">第</rb><rt style="box-sizing: border-box;">だい</rt></ruby>一のいましめである。<br>
